469
00:35:53,543 --> 00:35:54,913
Saudara Ahn Oh Ju.

470
00:35:56,043 --> 00:35:59,284
Foto itu dirilis
baru-baru ini lewat media.

471
00:36:00,284 --> 00:36:01,554
Andakah orang
yang ada di foto tersebut?

472
00:36:11,663 --> 00:36:13,293
Benar saya.

473
00:36:16,494 --> 00:36:18,634
Lantas bagaimana dengan 
orang yang ada di dalam mobil?

474
00:36:19,134 --> 00:36:20,534
Siapa dia?

475
00:36:23,873 --> 00:36:25,543
Hakim...

476
00:36:27,974 --> 00:36:29,674
...yang duduk di bangku hakim saat ini...

477
00:36:30,614 --> 00:36:33,443
...Hakim Cha Moon Sook.

478
00:36:39,523 --> 00:36:43,623
Berarti foto itu tidak dimanipulasi, benar?

479
00:36:43,623 --> 00:36:46,023
Pengacara Bong Sang Pil./ 
